column5: Ran into a good old (and I mean old...lol) friend from the board today! It was great seeing you Ron and catching up a bit. Too bad work gets in the way, haha! Glad to see you are still starting poopy in the lovely 'Burg!!!
Well looky, looky who showed up, Snady    Miss ya girl!!!!  thanks for bringing her out Ron  So, where's that invitation to your new place S?
Dang now there's a nice name to see on the board again. How's the musky season going this year?
